# Leave unset in local dev: API calls use /api via Vite proxy (works on LAN by IP).
# Set for production build or `vite preview`, e.g. http://192.168.1.10:3002
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3002

# Optional: gateway URL for the dev proxy (default http://127.0.0.1:3002)
# VITE_API_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:3002

# Daily dev on the dev PC: leave unset, open http://localhost:5174/login
# Phone / other LAN devices: run `pnpm dev:lan`, open http://<wlan-ip>:5174/login (IP only)
# Troubleshooting: `pnpm lan:check`
# Do not open the LAN IP in the dev PC browser — Windows hairpin often resets the connection.
